     Done HB.
    </comment>

<note><title>Note</title>
 <Para> 
  There is apparently a PPPoA beta program underway
  based on the Efficient Networks SpeedStream 3060/3061 (PCI, ADSL/DMT).
  Efficient is working with kernel developers, and reportedly this program is
  in late beta at this time. The initial release will be binary only drivers,
  but open source may follow. This is a big improvement! 

 </Para>
</note>

</Sect3>

